text: I attended the Agape JW Parents' Day X SSDB event and had a great time. The event was well-organized and engaging. I especially liked the zumba dance session for the kids and the games we participated in together. It really strengthened our bond with the school community. I'm looking forward to more events like this in the future!

Agape JW Parents' Day X SSDB event. We had a wonderful time and experience. It was well-organized and fun! Love the zumba dance and games. Overall, we left the event feeling more connected to the school community and reassured about my child's education. I look forward to attending more events like this in the future.

Thanks to all Agape JW teachers for organising the wonderful Parent's Day celebration on a Saturday. We all have so much fun. I am always amazed by the dedication put in by the teachers to organise these events. Thanks! My kids are blessed to have you guys.
